entry.title: How New York and California Botched Marijuana Legalization
entry.content: Steep taxes and heavy regulation are making it hard for licensed pot sellers to operate in some states, driving more producers and buyers to illegal outlets. ‘Our No. 1 competitor is the illicit market.’

entry.title: Russian Missile Barrage Kills at Least 23 in Ukraine
entry.content: Russia targeted cities across Ukraine in the most severe missile barrage in more than a month, as the Kremlin called for expanding the development and use of drones.
